</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="top" align="left">Prepare to eliminate the <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub></m:mrow></m:math> term by multiplying the top equation by <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>−1</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><newline/>Add the equations.</entry>
