<row>
<entry/>
<entry valign="top" align="center" namest="c2" nameend="c3">The first term is <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math><newline/>The common difference is <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></entry>
