<entry/>
<entry valign="top" align="center" namest="c2" nameend="c3"><para id="fs-id1167835343210">The general term of the sequence is <m:math><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mi>n</m:mi></m:msub><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para>
